{"tid":945240,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"平安夜，單身人士大行動","createTime":"2018-12-17T17:08:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-17T17:30:30.000Z","uid":150979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4cf8f92feaf6fa69921487c34d0a8ed7a691fd42","tid":945240,"uid":150979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T17:08:33.000Z","msg":"平安夜，又係一眾朋友，帶住男女朋友進行性交既日子。<br />\n<br />\n每一年，我都相當怨恨！<br />\n怨恨自己無份<br />\n怨恨自己無用<br />\n<br />\n正所謂，「人有我有」，「我無人無」，前者我係無可能有，我就要做後者。<br />\n我無得扑，你地都無呀，哇哈哈哈哈哈！！！！！！！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我而家正式召集單身人士，book 曬自己區既時鐘酒店，等佢地慾火焚身！<br />\n到佢地係街忍唔住，我地就要影相喇，嘻嘻。"},{"pid":"ae21a5ed3ba60843b9ed8c55be927bd0d4ef0ff4","tid":945240,"uid":65256,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T17:09:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j5NEzDu.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj5NEzDu.gif&h=803837f3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2201662091ddb08ed47b2d7ae9d673743bc16ce1","tid":945240,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T17:09:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f0ca915e2c12d4a911eb40f14c32d18c54341eb","tid":945240,"uid":197052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T17:10:16.000Z","msg":"啲酒店錢你比返我？"},{"pid":"332e876ca8acd0c64533d0228e37b4b66e30a214","tid":945240,"uid":150979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae21a5ed3ba60843b9ed8c55be927bd0d4ef0ff4","tid":945240,"uid":65256,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T17:09:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j5NEzDu.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj5NEzDu.gif&h=803837f3&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T17:11:08.000Z","msg":"book喇，起身做野"},{"pid":"ab24370bc47f7ce714763dedac0fe882266d8082","tid":945240,"uid":150979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f0ca915e2c12d4a911eb40